On Wed, 28 Nov 2007, James M. wrote:

> I want to make the seats in my '77 Westy electrically heated, has
> anybody done this?  How did you do it? How much did you spend?

I just put a truckers (bought at truck stop) electric seat cover on
that is plugged into lighter (I had to add that too) works pretty
well, doesn't get "hot" but rather just barely gets warm but it keeps
your butt comfy

paid about $35 3-4 years ago

Bob


